###

### OHLCV data for NVDA (weekly)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ohlcv/NVDA?timeframe=weekly

###

### OHLCV data for NVDA (monthly)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ohlcv/NVDA?timeframe=monthly

###

### Indicator data for NVDA (daily)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/indicators/NVDA?timeframe=daily

###

### Indicator data for AAPL (weekly)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/indicators/AAPL?timeframe=weekly

###

### Fundamental ratios for NVDA
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/fundamentals/NVDA

###

### Dashboard summary (all tickers, single request)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/dashboard/summary

###

